OL,3,CMouth painting artist sees Christmas
OL,4,Ccard design brought to life
OL,6,FA disabled mouth painting artist from
OL,7,FSouthampton has seen his artwork
OL,8,Ftransformed into a Christmas card for
OL,9,Fthe first time.
OL,11,FRob Trent paints using his mouth due
OL,12,Fto arthrogryposis - a condition
OL,13,Faffecting the joints and muscles which
OL,14,Fprevents him from using his hands or
OL,15,Ffeet.
OL,17,FHe said: "I think people are
OL,18,Fsurprised, not just because I'm doing
OL,19,Fit with my mouth, but hopefully the
OL,20,Fquality of the work stands out by
OL,21,Fitself as well."
