OL,3,CMouth painting artist sees Christmas
OL,4,Ccard design brought to life
OL,6,FHe has been painting with his mouth
OL,7,Fsince childhood and this year his
OL,8,FChristmas card design of a robin was
OL,9,Fselected to be a part of the Mouth and
OL,10,FFoot Painting Artists' (MFPA) 2025
OL,11,Fcollection.
OL,13,FMr Trent had the opportunity to go
OL,14,Fbehind the scenes and travel to
OL,15,Ffactories in Rochdale and Liverpool to
OL,16,Ffollow the journey of his Christmas
OL,17,Fcard.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
