OL,3,CMouth painting artist sees Christmas
OL,4,Ccard design brought to life
OL,6,FHe was able to see his design brought
OL,7,Fto life from the canvas, to the
OL,8,Fprinting press and to the assembling
OL,9,Fstage as it was prepared to be
OL,10,Fdistributed across the UK.
OL,12,FHe said: "I travelled 300 miles to
OL,13,Fwatch my Robin being turned into a
OL,14,Fcard. It is an experience I'll never
OL,15,Fforget.
