OL,3,CMouth painting artist sees Christmas
OL,4,Ccard design brought to life
OL,6,F"My little Robin - created over many
OL,7,Fweeks in my studio - entered this huge
OL,8,Fcard production factory that is
OL,9,Fprinting all sorts of things. I've
OL,10,Fnever seen a production line in
OL,11,Foperation before. It was incredible.
OL,13,F"I just hope people like the cards
OL,14,Fwhen they get them. Sending cards is
OL,15,Fgoing out of fashion, but let's
OL,16,Freignite that and what better way to
OL,17,Fsay happy Christmas to someone by
OL,18,Fsending them a card."
