OL,3,CMouth painting artist sees Christmas
OL,4,Ccard design brought to life
OL,6,FMr Trent is a member of the MFPA which
OL,7,Fis a collective group of disabled
OL,8,Fartists who paint using their mouths
OL,9,For feet.
OL,11,FThey fund their livelihoods through
OL,12,Fthe sale of reproductions of their
OL,13,Foriginal artworks.
OL,15,FHe added: "These sales enable us to
OL,16,Fgenerate an income and live
OL,17,Findependently. Like many other MFPA
OL,18,Fmembers know, generating a livelihood
OL,19,Fis a challenge when you're disabled.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
