OL,3,CMouth painting artist sees Christmas
OL,4,Ccard design brought to life
OL,6,F"But, by working together, the artists
OL,7,Fin the MFPA support each other -
OL,8,Fthrough the sale of our work we help
OL,9,Feach other live independent lives.
OL,11,F"It is incredibly empowering and
OL,12,Frewarding to see our artwork designs
OL,13,Fbrought to life as cards and know that
OL,14,Fthey bring happiness and joy to the
OL,15,Fpeople who buy them."
